{"tid":1591604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"612基金信託人開LIVE預告！","createTime":"2019-09-24T08:31:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T18:18:00.000Z","uid":294440,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f39e46fbc628284bd31533005e5e85ce6949c8dc","tid":1591604,"uid":294440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T08:31:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BxOXKbR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBxOXKbR.jpg&h=96d89d43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【 612基金信託人LIVE！】<br />\n<br />\n感謝大家對612人道支援基金一直以來的信任、支持以及各種寶貴的意見，等我們可以更加廣泛地支援在反送中運動中受傷或被捕的朋友！<br />\n<br />\n我地會係聽晚係基金專頁開LIVE，由許寶強、何韻詩兩位基金信託人親身講解基金的工作範圍、回答大家的提問及意見，以便大家更了解基金的工作，亦都讓大家能夠作出監察。<br />\n<br />\n詳情如下︰<br />\n2019年9月25日（三）<br />\n晚上9時正<br />\n612人道支援基金Facebook直播<br />\n基金信託人 - 許寶強、何韻詩<br />\n<br />\n問題收集︰<br />\n我們希望預先收集大家的意見及疑問，如大家希望信託人可以回答大家的提問，可預先將問題留言到本帖，讓工作人員整理。請留意，切勿將個人資料、行動詳情以公開發問形式發問，如有求助，請以直接以電話/Whatsapp/Telergram聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n612基金工作簡報（截至9月20日）：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/368482457185258/posts/419557388744431/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F368482457185258%2Fposts%2F419557388744431%2F&d=CxVPqDM3fecqSGKEY7rAqHhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=c21f24d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/368482457185258/posts/419557388744431/</a><br />\n<br />\n612人道支援基金申請 ／ 查詢︰98456641"},{"pid":"0f9362b97062f8033786630a511182df1b9e7c67","tid":1591604,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T08:33:57.000Z","msg":"有咩直接問，好過係度洗板"},{"pid":"a60f0598e1974f8e5fd7c075dcf828f862fa9db5","tid":1591604,"uid":140354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T08:33:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abfcc1b0f4c84eb4a3ce25bf2ea36ceb2c38c2c8","tid":1591604,"uid":38572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T08:34:53.000Z","msg