r />\n- 係616籌錢前, 有冇公開表明過「當日籌款金額係會扣除部分民陣開支」?</span><br />\n<br />\n基金工作簡報, 有列出法律、醫療等等支援個案數字。<br />\n但係一直都有傳聞, 612基金好難申請, 又或者申請好耐。<br />\n我想知道:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">- 可唔可以公開「總申請個案數字」, 「成功申請個案數字」及「駁回申請個案數字」?<br />\n- 可唔可以公開平均審批時間?</span><br />\n<br />\n諗到再問 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ba244dff597eec0df758078ad45e3fb5803b58","tid":1591604,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:58:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a27516b5ba2c43f3754928f29f5db002d13de59c","tid":1591604,"uid":90306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T10:28:18.000Z","msg":"幫612推"},{"pid":"1c8e6fa337e49cdbb5e64b8b9db50d6444110a79","tid":1591604,"uid":185854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T10:29:26.000Z","msg":"推問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dbf6ffde4483e36a84a6fd4cae3fb3a6bcd06c6","tid":1591604,"uid":294440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T12:52:04.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a1055e0e44bb2a413eedf92af9bad7bde28d7938","tid":1591604,"uid":324686,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T13:02:59.000Z","msg":"我淨係想知<br />\n有義士需要金錢上既支援<br />\n會唔會批<br />\n包括台灣義士<br />\n如果會 幾耐可以批到<br />\n如果冇錢食飯都要等一個月批就冇野好講"},{"pid":"8e36e7841188b80d540084c6d50be3c05e50fd78","tid":1591604,"uid":90306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:51:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"924bbda76f01e5d51fbf04f6b5eaa8886a68399d","tid":1591604,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1055e0e44bb2a413eedf92af9bad7bde28d7938","tid":1591604,"uid":324686,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"repl